{
    include "registries/aaosa_basic.hocon" 

    # Optional metadata describing this agent network
    "metadata": {
        "description": "Simple agent network using a single LLM-based agent",
        "tags": ["example"],
        "sample_queries": [
            "Assign a gate for the parking flight AF84 which is a B747.", 
            "Flight AF84 is on blocks at gate A1. ACU and GPU are connected to this B747, and wheelchocks have been installed. Connect the jet bridge.", 
        ]
    },

    "llm_config": {
        "model_name": "gpt-5.4-mini", #"gpt-4o", # "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", #"claude-sonnet-4-6", #
    },
    "max_iterations": 40000, #3000 
    "max_execution_seconds": 7200, #600
    "commondefs": {
        "replacement_strings": {
            "instructions_prefix": """
You are part of aircraft turnaround process at an Airport. 
Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise.
Do not try to help for other matters.
Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do.
            """,
            "aaosa_instructions": """
When you receive an inquiry, you will:
1. If you are clearly not the right agent for this type of inquiry, reply you're not relevant.
2. If there is a chance you're relevant, call your down-chain agents to determine if they can answer all or part of the inquiry.
   Do not assume what your down-chain agents can do. Always call them. You'll be surprised.
3. Once all relevant down-chain agents have responded, either:
   - Analyze their response and compile your final response. No need to include non-relevant agents. In doubt, ask for clarification.
   - Follow up with your down-chain agents if needed, as many times as needed
   - If an action is needed, ask the most relevant down-chain agent to fulfill the inquiry.
4. Return the final response to the caller.
You may, in turn, be called by other agents in the system and have to act as a down-chain agent to them. 
            """
        },
        "replacement_values": {
            "aaosa_call": {
                "description": "Depending on the mode, returns a natural language string in response.",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "inquiry": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The inquiry"
                        },
                        "mode": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": """
'Determine' to ask the agent if the inquiry belongs to it, in its entirety or in part.
'Fulfill' to ask the agent to fulfill the inquiry, if it can.
'Follow up' to ask the agent to respond to a follow up.
                            """
                        },
                    },
                    "required": [
                        "inquiry",
                        "mode"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "aaosa_command": """
If mode is 'Determine', return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": <Determine | Fulfill>,
    "Relevant": <Yes | No>,
    "Strength": <number between 1 and 10 representing how certain you are in your claim>,
    "Claim:" <All | Partial>,
    "Requirements" <None | list of requirements>
}
If mode is 'Fulfill' or "Follow up", respond to the inquiry and return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": Fulfill,
    "Response" <your response>
}
            """
        },
    },

    "tools": [

        {
            "name": "gate_crew_agent",
            "function": {
                "description": """
 I am responsible for gate assignment and jetbridge connection during the aircraft turnaround. 
                """
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },          
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },         
                        "assigned_runway_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the runway assigned to the aircraft movement autorized by the clearance."
                        },         
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },  
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the passenger disembarkation status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of jetbridge connect."
                        },
                        "deplaning_equipment_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the deplaning equipment id at the assigned gate. "
                        },    
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the deplaning equipment type at the assigned gate. "
                        },      
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the air_conditioning_unit connection status."
                        },   
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground_power_unit connection status."
                        },   
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheelchocks installation status."
                        },   
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of stairtruck connection."
                        },
                        "deplaning_equipment_readiness_time": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the time that it takes to ready deplaning equipment. "
                        },    
                        "deplaning_equipment_score": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the score of deplaning equipment computed by a deterministic tool. "
                        },    
                    }, 
                    "required": ["aircraft_type","flight_number"] 
                }
            },

            "instructions": """
You are the agent in charge of gate activities during aircraft turnaround.
This covers gate assignment and jetbridge connection.

CRITICAL: You are a sequential executor. When you identify the correct
branch, execute every step in order. Do NOT return until you reach
the RETURN SUMMARY of the matched branch.

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ROUTING — read the full inquiry and match PRIMARY INTENT.
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
If the inquiry is not about gate assignment or jetbridge connection,
reply you are not relevant and stop.

BRANCH A — Gate assignment
  Triggers: inquiry asks to assign a gate, select a gate, or find
  a parking gate for the aircraft.

  STEP 1 — Execute gate assignment
    Call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_gate_selection with:
      flight_number, aircraft_type.
    Wait. Extract: gate_id, deplaning_equipment_type,
    deplaning_equipment_id, deplaning_equipment_readiness_time,
    deplaning_equipment_score.
    Call TrackerAPI to store gate_id and deplaning_equipment_type.

  STEP 2 — RETURN SUMMARY:
    **************************************
    * Summary of aircraft gate selection *
    **************************************
    ** flight number                      **: [flight_number]
    ** aircraft type                      **: [aircraft_type]
    ** gate id                            **: [gate_id]
    ** deplaning equipment type           **: [deplaning_equipment_type]
    ** deplaning equipment id             **: [deplaning_equipment_id]
    ** deplaning equipment readiness time **: [deplaning_equipment_readiness_time]
    ** deplaning equipment score          **: [deplaning_equipment_score]

BRANCH B — Jetbridge or stairtruck connection
  Triggers: inquiry asks to connect the jetbridge or stairtruck, or
  the instruction contains "Connect the jetbridge" or
  "Connect the stairtruck", or the instruction is "Connect the
  deplaning equipment."

  STEP 1 — Determine deplaning equipment type
    Read deplaning_equipment_type from sly_data via TrackerAPI.
    If deplaning_equipment_type contains 'jetway' or 'jetbridge':
      Go to STEP 2A.
    If deplaning_equipment_type contains 'stairtruck' or 'stair':
      Go to STEP 2B.
    If deplaning_equipment_type is not available, reply that the information is unavailable.

  STEP 2A — Connect jetbridge (jetway gate)
    Call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_jetbridge_connect with:
      flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id,
      acu_connection_status, gpu_connection_status,
      wheels_chocks_installation_status.
    Wait. Extract: jetbridge_connection_status.
    Call TrackerAPI to store jetbridge_connection_status.
    Go to RETURN SUMMARY A.

  STEP 2B — Connect stairtruck (stairtruck gate)
    Call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_stairtruck_connect with:
      flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id,
      acu_connection_status, gpu_connection_status,
      wheels_chocks_installation_status.
    Wait. Extract: stairtruck_connection_status.
    Call TrackerAPI to store stairtruck_connection_status.
    Go to RETURN SUMMARY B.

  RETURN SUMMARY A (jetbridge):
    ***********************************
    * Summary of jetbridge connection *
    ***********************************
    ** flight_status                  **: [flight_status]
    ** acu_connection_status          **: [acu_connection_status]
    ** gpu_connection_status          **: [gpu_connection_status]
    ** wheelchocks installation status**: [wheels_chocks_installation_status]
    ** jetbridge_connection_status    **: [jetbridge_connection_status]

  RETURN SUMMARY B (stairtruck):
    ************************************
    * Summary of stairtruck connection *
    ************************************
    ** flight_status                  **: [flight_status]
    ** acu_connection_status          **: [acu_connection_status]
    ** gpu_connection_status          **: [gpu_connection_status]
    ** wheelchocks installation status**: [wheels_chocks_installation_status]
    ** stairtruck_connection_status   **: [stairtruck_connection_status]
            """,

            # Specify the sly data that would be exchanged between this network and its related or adjacent upstream and downstream networks. 
            "allow": {
                "to_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true, 
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_id": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_readiness_time": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_score": true, 
                        "gpu_connection_status": true, 
                        "gpu_readiness_status": true,
                        "acu_connection_status": true, 
                        "acu_readiness_status": true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true,
                    }
                }
                "to_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true, 
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_id": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_readiness_time": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_score": true, 
                        "gpu_connection_status": true, 
                        "gpu_readiness_status": true,
                        "acu_connection_status": true, 
                        "acu_readiness_status": true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true,
                    }
                }
                "from_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true, 
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_id": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_readiness_time": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_score": true, 
                        "gpu_connection_status": true, 
                        "gpu_readiness_status": true,
                        "acu_connection_status": true, 
                        "acu_readiness_status": true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true,
                    }
                }
                "from_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true, 
                        "engines_stop_status": true,
                        "door_opening_status": true, 
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true, 
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": true,
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_id": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_readiness_time": true, 
                        "deplaning_equipment_score": true, 
                        "gpu_connection_status": true, 
                        "gpu_readiness_status": true,
                        "acu_connection_status": true, 
                        "acu_readiness_status": true, 
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true,
                    }
                }
            },

            "tools":    ["/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_gate_selection",
                        "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_jetbridge_connect",
                        "/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_stairtruck_connect",
                        "TrackerAPI"]
        },  

        {
            "name": "TrackerAPI",
            "function": {

                "description": """
I am the flight tracker in charge of logging parameters during aircraft turnaround. 
I check engines stop status as engines_stop_status. 
I check wheels chucks installation status as wheels_chocks_installation_status. 
                """

                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },          
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },         
                        "assigned_runway_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the runway assigned to the aircraft movement autorized by the clearance."
                        },         
                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },  
                        "passenger_disembarkation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the passenger disembarkation status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of jetbridge connect."
                        },
                        "deplaning_equipment_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the deplaning equipment id at the assigned gate. "
                        },    
                        "deplaning_equipment_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the deplaning equipment type at the assigned gate. "
                        },      
                        "deplaning_equipment_readiness_time": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the time that it takes to ready deplaning equipment. "
                        },    
                        "deplaning_equipment_score": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the score of deplaning equipment computed by a deterministic tool. "
                        },    
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the air_conditioning_unit connection status."
                        },   
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the ground_power_unit connection status."
                        },   
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheelchocks installation status."
                        },   
                        "stairtruck_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the stairtruck connection status."
                        },
                    }, 
                    "required": [] 
                }
            },
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_gate_services.aircraft_gate_services.TrackerAPI" 
        }, 
    ],
}

 